data.title: Mota-Engil Central Europe S.A.
data.meta_description:
Mota-Engil Central Europe S.A. is one of the leading companies in the construction industry in Poland.


Mota-Engil Central Europe SA is part of the international Mota-Engil Group. 
Activities of the Group are diversified and global. The company is present in 21 countries on 3 continents - Europe, Africa and Latin America, and always meets the rigorous standards of quality and potential necessary to carry out investments in each of these markets.

In Poland, the company has been operating for 18 years and is engaged in areas of road, bridge, railway and general construction. The company is also active in fields of electricity works, mining and real estate. Through all these years Mota-Engil Central Europe has built many miles of highways and expressways, but also residential complexes and public buildings.
